<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
<p>B. E. Allen was manager of the Woodlands Division of the Union Bag-Camp Corp. in Savannah, Georgia.  He was also active in his professional organization, the Society of American Foresters serving as vice-president and council member.</p>
</bioghist>



<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>The collection consists of correspondence and other materials relating to forest land use and his activities with the Society of American Foresters.</p>
</scopecontent>

